03:02.938 --> 03:05.996
Uh, Caitlyn Jenner hadn't happened.

03:06.021 --> 03:07.806
Bathroom laws hadn't started.

03:07.843 --> 03:11.610
So, I just thought that
Kai was extremely feminine.

03:11.645 --> 03:13.745
Between the ages of two and four,

03:13.781 --> 03:16.648
Kai started playing with girls,
and thought boys were yucky.

03:16.673 --> 03:20.351
It's at that age when Kai
wanted a tutu and not a truck.

03:20.921 --> 03:23.987
Kai: These are just my dress-up dresses.

03:24.012 --> 03:26.401
This one is Rapunzel.

03:26.426 --> 03:28.360
Rapunzel?

