before you actually did?

10:54.883 --> 10:57.202
Like, I think like...

10:57.303 --> 10:59.903
- 245.
- (laughs softly)

11:00.087 --> 11:03.481
So, I got really excited,
and I went to Hounds,

11:03.506 --> 11:06.520
which is an only men's barbershop,

11:06.545 --> 11:09.604
and... cut my hair.

11:09.629 --> 11:11.930
How did things change
once you got your hair cut?

11:12.904 --> 11:14.703
My life changed,

11:14.794 --> 11:16.928
'cause I felt good in my skin.

11:17.104 --> 11:18.878
What are you gonna do tomorrow?

11:18.903 --> 11:21.873
