see if I need hormone blockers.

11:21.908 --> 11:25.604
Max, why is it so important that
you get the hormone blockers?

11:25.931 --> 11:28.598
So I don't go through girls' puberty.

11:28.623 --> 11:30.768
I don't want that to happen.

11:31.733 --> 11:34.682
Toboni: Has Max started to
talk about puberty at all?

11:34.707 --> 11:37.833
He knows about puberty,
about female puberty.

11:37.858 --> 11:40.958
He started to have some
breast growth last year, um,

11:40.994 --> 11:43.053
and he, actually, was using Band-Aids

11:43.078 --> 11:45.306
to try to cover himself up.

11:46.026 --> 11:48.423
He's eight, you know.

11:48.448 --> 11:51.602
And, in general, how do you
feel about hormone blockers?

11:51.637 --> 11:55.239
Nervous about it a little
bit, just because I always...

11:55.446 --> 11:57.688
like to know a little bit more
about medical intervention,

11:57.713 --> 12:00.143
you know, and anytime
we're introducing chemicals

12:00.178 --> 12:02.579
into bodies that, you know,
weren't there naturally.

12:02.604 --> 12:05.148
I'm just, kind of, a
little bit worried about it.

12:05.183 --> 12:06.536
So, that's on my mind.

12:06.561 --> 12:08.986
Toboni: <i>Max goes to
Boston Children's Hospital</i>

12:09.021 --> 12:12.122
<i>which opened the first clinic
for transgender youth in the US.</i>

12:12.157 --> 12:14.515
- Woman: Max O'Brien?
- Toboni: <i>Since 2007,</i>

12:14.540 --> 12:17.293
<i>they've treated hundreds
of children and teens.</i>

12:17.329 --> 12:20.696
In the past couple years, our
volume has just about doubled.

12:20.732 --> 12:22.685
Toboni: <i>Dr. Jeremi
Carswell is the director</i>

12:22.710 --> 12:24.270
<i>of the gender program here.</i>

12:24.295 --> 12:25.835
What are hormone blockers?

12:25.870 --> 12:28.670
It's a hormone that will block

12:28.695 --> 12:31.007
the progression of puberty.

12:31.042 --> 12:32.654
We can give it in a
couple different forms.

12:32.679 --> 12:34.276
It's an implantable device,

12:34.311 --> 12:36.655
or it's an injection
and it's reversible.

12:36.680 --> 12:38.652
Max, I'm gonna have you hop on up here.

12:40.637 --> 12:42.084
Okay, just look at me.

12:42.119 --> 12:44.720
Toboni: <i>What are the downsides,
or what are the adverse effects</i>

12:44.756 --> 12:48.157
<i>of getting hormone blockers, when
you're, you know, say Max's age?</i>

12:48.192 --> 12:51.793
Carswell: <i>We have concerns,
about primarily, bone health,</i>

12:51.828 --> 12:54.396
because the sex steroids,
estrogen and testosterone,

12:54.432 --> 12:57.499
really do help build those
bones to be nice and strong.

12:57.535 --> 13:00.897
Another one is, really, kind
of the psychosocial development.

13:00.922 --> 13:02.504
Our brains are supposed to be ex...

13:02.540 --> 13:05.373
you know, exposed to
estrogen and testosterone.

13:05.408 --> 13:07.210
<i>You know, if you're not
getting your sex steroids,</i>

13:07.235 --> 13:08.342
<i>do you still go through that?</i>

13:08.378 --> 13:11.866
And how important is that
in gender identification?

13:11.901 --> 13:12.991
We don't know.

13:13.016 --> 13:14.673
That's it! You're done!

13:16.391 --> 13:19.237
I do think that puberty
has actually started.

13:19.262 --> 13:20.474
Um, the labs do show...

13:20.499 --> 13:21.956
- really early puberty.
- I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

13:21.991 --> 13:23.924
I... I think we can move forward.

13:23.960 --> 13:26.026
- Okay.
- Do you want to see what it looks like?

13:26.957 --> 13:29.074
See this little thing? Okay?

13:29.099 --> 13:32.166
This is the Histrelin implant.

13:32.202 --> 13:34.981
Are you gonna put it
in my skin as a shot?

13:35.006 --> 13:37.337
It actually goes right about here.

13:37.372 --> 13:38.914
This is what it feels
like when it's inside.

13:38.939 --> 13:40.007
Okay.

